summary.description:
Today, cooler for the outside temperature (down 2.6°C) and feels like temperature (down 2.4°C), more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 10%), and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.8 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 723 m), light levels (up 10831 lux), and pressure (down 9 mbar).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 10976 lux), cloud levels (up 1166 m), feels like temperature (up 4.8°C), and outside temperature (up 3.7°C) when compared to today.
